ed to the spectral distribution variability of the backlighter\nduring the radiographic pulse. Numerically, that distribution is strongly\ndependent upon NLTE models and it could potentially be used as a mean to\ndiscriminate among them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 May 2017 12:31:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
